text: Brenda Starr is a comic strip (1940-2011) about a female reporter. Brenda Starr may also refer to: * Brenda Starr (1976 film), an American made-for- television adventure film based on the comic strip * Brenda Starr (1989 film), a film based on the comic strip * Brenda Starr, Reporter (film), a 1945 film serial based on the comic strip * Brenda K.
